snippet.title: Best VGM 1344 - Castlevania : Lords of Shadow - Final Confrontation (Short Version)
snippet.description:
Live version: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zuW2Yf4-GB8

See also:
Best VGM 861 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6AZLmFaSpR0

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3
Castlevania : Lords of Shadow (2009)
Final Confrontation (Short Version)
Oscar Araujo
